  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to examine whether the ear acupoint stimulation is effective on obese
      women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      % change body weight, BMI, lipid profile, glucose and obese hormone.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
